Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,挺起胸膛 好不容易才卸下了伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 是「恶之花」封面上的画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个画到地板上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是春日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那间教室也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的体操服也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都是春日干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不会分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是绝对不会分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 可是 可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,春日你讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你再好好考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我是这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你去跟春日说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,说佐伯想和你做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白春日是怎么想的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是高男做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 气死我了 我家暂时禁止我外出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我家很可能也会这么干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖的走人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯太可怜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那套体操服要怎么处理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 哥去用空气枪把变态抓起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,做得到就去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,高男 回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,学校那边没事吧 听说变态又出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,学校保安都是干什么吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样别说是学习了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,高男？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不舒服 上去休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不讨厌我 佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我是这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,远走他乡 到个谁都不认识我的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,青木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,奥田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,春日…感冒休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,木下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,乡田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在别的教室总有种违和感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听说我们的教室正在打扫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都知道吗 春日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,说想要和我做朋友又是为什么 骗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是 单纯闲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你去跟春日说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说佐伯想和春日你做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 什… 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你就是一脸想做爱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看春日会露出什么表情 就告诉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村和春日是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他和我订下了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为春日是个无可救药的大变态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们就订下契约 把他的真面目扒个一干二净！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么… 怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,春日不是什么变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过无论从哪个角度看他都是个变态呢 这个小镇里最变态的
Comment: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B PART====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,高男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 我削了个苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你从昨天开始就什么都没吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,高男 妈妈有些事想问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫佐伯 和春日同班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,高男 有个叫佐伯的孩子来探望…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再等等 跟她说再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？等什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 跟她说我还不能见她！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊 高男他感冒好像还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,春日你听得到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,春日为什么会做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白春日是怎么想的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起… 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,体操服的事情 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是很高兴的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,春日…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你那么做是因为心里想我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,听说男孩子都是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,反而难过的是你把这件事瞒着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你告诉我！跟我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别去跟仲村说 跟我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我明白 春日你在想些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明天来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,高男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么 好好的跟妈妈坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这件衣服混在了洗衣机里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你干了什么才能脏成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是高男做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高男！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我的容身之处…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市里没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来得太晚了 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别不说话 说点有趣的事来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,爸妈全都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经哪都回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,家 学校 佐伯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,高男！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,高男！在的话就吱一声！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,高男！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,高男！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是春日的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,像个傻瓜一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去… 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,「另一边」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,春日前段时间像个臭老鼠一样把这个丢掉 从我面前逃走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,「不想让我说出去的话」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「你带我 去那座山的另一边」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有继续留在这恶心的城市里的理由吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村 你愿意跟我一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你跟着我啦 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 春日夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我的儿子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,高男他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没… 只是他突然跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么 谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
